<DATE>08/17/2009</DATE>
<AUTHOR>Bowers</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>Bought this after looking at the Ford, Nissan, Chevy, and Hyundai models that compete. With the $3,200 GM rebate and the $4,500 "clunker cash" rebate, we drove out way below the other models. Only 600 miles on it so far. Suspension seems tight, handling is sporty, interior is gorgeous, exterior is very appealing. Getting 25 mpg in town. Have not been on the interstate yet. Love the XM satellite radio and the built-in phone. Also have the OnStar. Just touch a button to activate the phone and speak out the number! Wonderful machine. Our 3rd Pontiac and loving it!</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>XM radio; hands-free phone; OnStar system; sporty ride and handling.</FAVORITE>
